sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Emp as Employer / Verifier
    participant FE as Verify Portal
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant BC as Blockchain

    Note over Emp,FE: Path A — scan QR / enter ID
    Emp->>FE: Scan QR -> /verify/{transcriptId}
    FE->>API: GET /api/verify/{transcriptId}
    API->>DB: Find transcript by id
    alt Not found
        DB-->>API: null
        API-->>FE: 404 { status: NOT_FOUND }
    else Found
        DB-->>API: transcript (sha256, txHash)
        API->>BC: verifyTranscript(id, sha256)
        BC-->>API: { isValid, isRevoked, issuedAt }
        API-->>FE: 200 { status: VALID|REVOKED|INVALID, details }
    end
    FE-->>Emp: Animated badge + student/institution/date

    Note over Emp,FE: Path B — upload the PDF
    Emp->>FE: Drop transcript PDF
    FE->>FE: Compute SHA-256 (crypto.subtle)
    FE->>API: POST /api/verify/upload (file)
    API->>DB: Find transcript by sha256
    API->>BC: verifyTranscript(id, sha256)
    BC-->>API: { isValid, isRevoked }
    API-->>FE: 200 { status, computedHash, details }
